flowRoot.flowPara: The back button is only shown if you switched from the viewer mode
The home view is displayed if EoG is started from its launcher
Image manipulation controls are displays when the pointer moves over the image. They fade out after a delay once the pointer has stopped moving
Image can be panned through click and drag. Cursor changes to a hand when over the image.
The gallery displays images from the source directory or, in the case of GNOME Documens, collection
Full screen and properties buttons (the latter toggles)
